doctor's offices smell weird.

and that is where i am right now..because of my stupid eye.and my allergies suck,and its just a sucky day.
i probably wont even be able to do anything tonight,even though i just had to go to my church lockin..but id rather do that than just sit at home.however i have a funny feeling thats exactly what im going to be doing
also,im running on about 3 hours of sleep right now.

last night was really weird for me..i found out stuff i didnt want to know,but maybe i needed to know it.i have realized that i need to talk about things more,even if i dont feel comfortable with it.i dont confront people about my feelings enough and i end up just keeping it inside.that doesnt really seem to work out for me either.
just last night..i realized how much i really dont like to associate with girls.online is ridiculous and i dont like talking to people on it because you cant tell how they're feeling,but i could just tell how fake nice girls can be.honestly,i was ripshit.and i dont hate a lot of people..i rarely even do,especially if i dont have a reason,but i can honestly say right now that i have a growing hate for this person.i just dont understand why girls cant just keep to themselves and not get themselves into other peoples business and try to ruin things just to make themselves feel better.if you really have that big of a problem take it up with the person directly,instead of making the people that are associated with them go through hell.last night was pretty much close to hell for me.
this is also another reason why i am so grateful for the close girl friends that i do have and that i know i can trust.everyone else is so lame.

im done for now.
who knows,i probably will have like 4 other entries today considering i have nothing else to do and i feel like i need to vent
